body:
Warmest of Places

Some days, much like this one, Harry feels cold and out of place. He had a meeting about his tour dates that was said to last about an hour, two. Tops, but something went wrong, the meeting lasted a god for saken 4 hours.

All he wanted to do was go back home to his girl waiting back home, but of course he wasn’t half stressed enough for Jeff to let him leave, he told him to continue writing and recording new songs for his upcoming album.

He would occasionally stop writing to check his phone. To text her and sometimes to look at pictures of her because god she was the only thing keeping him from snapping and coming home to her embrace.

Reading over the lyrics to a song he wrote, he noticed that he subconsciously wrote about her. There were references to her scattered all over the song, rather intimate references, there was no way on earth his fans would miss these references, but he couldn’t care less he was wrecked.

“Goodnight, guys” he made a half-assed waving motion towards the crew.

He couldn’t be bothered to listen to their replies. He got into his range rover, staying a moment before putting the key in the ignition, and driving home once the engine roared to life.

“Princess, daddy’s home” he said non-chalantly, a smile cracking once he hears his girl running down to greet him.

She hugged him tightly and then asked him “How was your day?” When she broke away from the hug.

“Tiring” he replied with a sigh.

“Do you want me to heat up the food?”

“No, not really hungry. I do need you to warm me up though” he said not bothering to look at her.

She stays dumbfounded for a few second and then she nods and goes to the bedroom while stripping.

“Good girl” he whispered as he poured himself a glass of whiskey while waiting for his girl to be ready.

When he got upstairs he find his girl laying on her side while naked, a sight that makes him flutter inside.

He unbuckles his belt taking off his jeans and boxers and spooning her like he’s the big spoon, as usual, he enters her with his eyes closed and mouth slightly opened as she moans at his massive size.

As he drifts to sleep he whispers into her ear “god, i love your cunt”
